title: Two Sides to Every Date "What He Had in His Pocket That Turned Her Off"
description: Rich had a date with Jen and thought it was great but on their second date, he knew there was trouble but didn't know what.  We spoke to Jen and learned that he pulled something out of his pocket during the date which ended up being a big turn off. The crazy part? He wasn't the ONLY one who does this.
